parameters: Shif: "Oh... you've come already? That was unexpected..."

Shif: "Heh heh heh... To think you can talk such nonsense in this
situation..."
Shif: "Heh heh heh... However... to be cornered by someone like you..."
Shif: "I can't do that... She's an important shrine maiden..."
Umi: "Don't lie, Banka! Umi won't be fooled!"
Kru: "What! What's going on... Shif... what have you done⁉"
Shif: "Now, now, don't panic... I've just cast a little hypnotic magic..."
Lutecia: "Ugh... Kru... Umi has been made to mistake Banka for Kru..."
Umi: "Shif! It doesn't matter what happens to Umi... save everyone else!"
Umi: "Ugh... what are you planning to do!"

Shif: "Now... Umi... watch carefully... Banka, you've done well until
now..."
Banka: "What do you mean, all of a sudden?"
Banka: "Guh... how could you... Chancellor Shif..."

Shif: "Hahaha... The sensation of stabbing this man... it always feels good
no matter how many times I do it..."
Shif: "Hah hah hah! How about that! Your beloved Kru is dead!"
Shif: "Hahahahaha! Now Lord Xecilray will be revived!"
Kru: "Wait‼‼ I won't let you go any further‼"

Shif: "You... You know that this misty substance is the door leading to
Lord Xecilray's body, don't you?"

Shif: "Kukukuku... Hahahahaha! I see! No wonder I thought something was
off!"

Shif: "Well... ever since you ran away, Umi disappeared too... The seal on
the Lutecia ruins was broken, and a rebellion started in the village...
Everything has been falling into place one after another, so I had a
hunch..."
Shif: "You... You're using the curse of time travel, aren't you?"
Lutecia: "...I knew it... You were aware..."

Shif: "Don't underestimate me... Though I must say, I only just learned
that such a curse actually exists..."

Kru: "So what... Right here, right now... I'll defeat you and it'll all be
over!"

Shif: "Hmph... This is why I dislike fools whose brains have turned to
muscle. Ha!"
Kru: "What the... What did you do?"
Shif: "Oh nothing... just changed the plan..."
Shif: "Oh... Lord Xecilray... at last, you make your appearance..."
Xecilray: "How dare you summon me to such a place..."
Shif: "Yes... It was an emergency situation..."

Xecilray: "Moreover... to prepare such a fake vessel... This girl is not
functioning as a vessel at all..."
Shif: "Yes... She's quite a stubborn one..."

Xecilray: "Fool‼‼ Making excuses! What's important is the fallen soul...
You will atone for this with your death!"
Xecilray: "What... My curse doesn't work on you!"
Shif: "...Yes... Whatever you do is futile."

Lutecia: "Probably... He's layered multiple counter-magic spells against
curses..."
Shif: "Now, Lord Xecilray... Let us overcome this hardship together..."
Shif: "You will live eternally within me..."
Xecilray: "Stop it-----! I'm being absorbed! I'm being absorbed!"
Xecilray: "Lutecia! Help me... please help me----"
Shif: "Such a poor loser... Even a god should not be so unsightly..."

Xecilray: "Grr... I curse you... I will curse you for all eternity within
you..."
Shif: "Hahaha... So this is what it feels like to become a god..."
Lutecia: "No way... This can't be happening..."
Iburu: "No... This curse power... It's too great..."

Shif: "Hahahaha... Hahahahaha! At last, I have obtained the power of a god!
It's not the amount of power I anticipated, but... it will do..."
Shif: "It's been long... so very long... But at last, I have arrived..."
Iburu: "It's no use... We can't possibly stand against this..."

Shif: "Now then... you insignificant humans... kneel and become my
sustenance..."

Captain of the Guard: "Chancellor Shif! By order of the king, you are to be
executed for treason against the state! Surrender peacefully!"

Captain of the Guard: "What's the matter! Are you frightened by our
numbers⁉"
Kru: "You... take your men and flee from here quickly."

Captain of the Guard: "Hmph! I have no reason to take orders from a
commoner like you! This is my chance for a promotion! I'll earn my merits
here and become a general!"

Shif: "Hahahahaha! This is delightful... Sorry, I couldn't help but laugh
at the sheer absurdity..."
Captain of the Guard: "How dare you show such disrespect!"

Shif: "Kukuku... To speak to me, a god, in such a manner... Don't think
you'll die easily..."
Captain of the Guard: "Enough talk! Everyone attack at once!"
Captain of the Guard: "This can't be... It had no effect at all..."
Shif: "Sigh... Are you satisfied now? Die."
Iburu: "This can't be... In an instant..."

Shif: "Hahahahaha! Are you so scared that you can't even speak? Kru... it's
your turn next!"
Shif: "Hahahaha! What can you possibly do?"
Shif: "Hmph! Clever trick! I'll make you pay for this!"
Shif "This... such a thing... as a god... I..."
Kru "Give it up, Shif... You're finished..."
Xecilray "Heh heh heh... It seems that's all the man you are..."
Shif "Guh! That voice... Xecilray... Ah! Stop it! Stop it!"
Xecilray "Heh heh heh... Your reign was short-lived..."

Lutecia "Surely Shif's magical power has weakened and he can no longer
control it."

Xecilray "Heh heh heh... Well... You've had your way for quite some time...
I'll take good care of you... Uuuu!"

Lutecia "Probably the damage has accumulated from the fight with Kru...
Surely his body can't hold up anymore..."
Xecilray "Uuuu... I hate this! I am immortal! This... such a thing...!"
Lutecia "Give up, Xecilray! Now, disappear with me!"
Xecilray "I don't want that... If it's come to this..."

Shif "Huh huh huh... With this curse power... If I have this much...
Haaaaaaaahhhhhhh!"
Lutecia "Dangerous! Let's get out of here!"
Kru: "I've found you, Shif! Your end is near!"

Shif: "Heh heh heh... To think that someone like you could corner me like
this..."
Banka: "Lord Shif... What should we do... We're going to be killed..."
Shif: "I can't do that... She's an important shrine maiden..."
Lutecia: "Stop this... It's pointless to go any further."

Shif: "Silence! How dare a brat like you get in my way... I didn't want to
resort to this method but..."

Shif: "Now, now, don't panic... I've merely cast a little hypnotic
magic..."

Umi: "Ah... huh? Umi... Kru's been captured too... But why am I wearing
clothes like Banka's?"
Kru: "Shif! What is this? What have you done⁉"
Lutecia: "It must be that Umi sees Banka as Kru... No way!"
Shif: "Now... Umi... watch closely... Banka, you've done well until now..."
Banka: "What do you mean, all of a sudden?"
Banka: "Guh... how could you... Lord Shif..."
Shif: "Hah hah hah! How about that! Your beloved Kru is dead!"
Shif: "Hahaha! With this, Lord Xecily will be revived!"

Xecily: "How dare you prepare such a sham vessel for me... This girl is not
functioning as a vessel at all..."

Shif: "But... her body has been trained and corrupted... I thought it would
please you..."

Xecily: "Fool‼‼ Such things are dime a dozen! What matters is a corrupted
soul... You will pay for this with your life!"

Lutecia: "Xecily! Go back to sleep peacefully... Stop meddling in the world
of children!"

Xecily: "Hmph... Who do you think you are, annoying Lutecia... This world
exists because I am in it..."

Lutecia: "Stop it... Xecily... No matter how much you struggle, you can no
longer incarnate in this world... I know this very well..."

Xecily: "Ha... how annoying... Ah, I'm so irritated... Worst wake-up
ever... Fine then... I'll destroy this area and create a new altar for
myself..."
Kru "No way... She's been taken over by Xecily..."
Xecily "Kukukuku... It's been a while since I've gone on a rampage..."
